    <h3 data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#featuresaccordion" data-target="#collapseThree">
      Bar Graph Problems
    </h3>
    <div class="collapse" id=collapseThree>
      <div class="accordion-inner">
        <p>Bar Graph problems are of 2 types. Withe you have to read from the bar graph like you would any other or you have to edit it. To any one bar, click on the top of the bar and pull either up or down. If the bar is on 0, click on the lower axis and pull up.</p>
        <br style="clear:both;">
      </div> 
