  <div class="accordion-group"> 
    <h3 data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#featuresaccordion" data-target="#collapseFour">
      Tally Marks Problems
    </h3>
    <div class="collapse" id=collapseFour>
      <div class="accordion-inner">
        <p>There are 2 types of tally marks problems. The first involves just reading from the table of tally marks. The other involves making a tally marks table. To do this, click on the "|" button to add a vertical mark and click on the "/" button to make the slash mark. To remove the last mark, click the third button.</p>
        <br style="clear:both;">
      </div> 
    </div>
