    </h3>
    <div class="collapse" id=collapseFive>
      <div class="accordion-inner">
        <p>The Number Line is very intuitive. Some problems will allow you to move the number line. You do this by clicking on it and dragging. Other problems will allow you to zoom in or out, which you can do with the bar on the left.You might have to name the number being pointed to on the number line or you may have to add or subtract numbers by dragging the pointer.</p>
